<emphasis box="[151,385,1409,1431]" italics="true" pageId="121" pageNumber="122">Pogonomyrmex stefani</emphasis>
Lattke, 2006: 53
</taxonomicName>
, figs. 1–4 (worker, male). Holotype worker [MIZA] (not examined). VENEZUELA, Bolívar: Fundo San Rafael, Río Víllacoa, 165 m, 6o25’N, 67o01’W, 6 December 2004 (J.E. Lattke leg. #2964). Paratypes examined—same data as holotype: 1 worker [MCZ], 1 worker, 1 male [MIZA].
</paragraph>
